    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 24 Creation Points</p><p>Drain: 20 CCD Chakra</p><p></p><p>Increase the cost of activating your S.N.B by the CCD Drain of this Upgrade. </p><p>You install a holographic projector into your Scientific Ninja Beast making it seem to be standing slightly further than it actually is. </p><p>Attack rolls against your S.N.B are made at disadvantage, if it is hit by an attack, it doesn't gain the benefit of this upgrade until the start of its next turn. </p><p>This upgrade also doesn't function if your S.N.B is incapacitated.</p>",
